rocheMainUserShowTooltipsToggle_init: {"MDX":"SELECT ({[}Clients].[$activeUser]}*{[zSYS Analogic User Parameter Measure].[ShowToolTipsFlag]})ON COLUMNS FROM [zSYS Analogic User Parameter]"}
rocheMainUserShowTooltipsToggle_launch: {"MDX":"UPDATE  CUBE [zSYS Analogic User Parameter] SET ([}Clients].[$activeUser],[zSYS Analogic User Parameter Measure].[ShowToolTipsFlag]) = $rocheMainUserShowTooltipsToggle_launch_value"}
rocheMainUserGridButton_init: {"MDX":"SELECT ({[}Clients].[$activeUser]}*{[zSYS Analogic User Parameter Measure].[FullName]})ON COLUMNS FROM [zSYS Analogic User Parameter]"}
rocheScrollTable_init_1: {"MDX": " WITH SET YearsSet AS {FILTER( {TM1FILTERBYLEVEL( {TM1SUBSETALL([YEAR])} ,0)} ,[Year].Currentmember.Name >= [BC Product Metadata].([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version],[Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname],[Measures BC Product Metadata].[PS Year]) AND [Year].Currentmember.Name <= [BC Product Metadata].([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version],[Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname],[Measures BC Product Metadata].[SE Year]))} MEMBER [Year].[EmptyOrNot] AS IIF(COUNT(YearsSet) = 0, '{[Year].[NA Year]}', 'YearsSet') SELECT {StrToSet([Year].[EmptyOrNot])} ON COLUMNS FROM [}ElementAttributes_Year] WHERE ([}ElementAttributes_Year].[Slider Label])"}
rocheScrollTable_init_2: {"MDX":" WITH SET [GlobalOrEmptySubsetname] AS '{TM1SubsetToSet ( [Line Item BC P&L Input], IIF ( ISEMPTY([BC Product Metadata].([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version],[Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname],[Measures BC Product Metadata].[Product Type])), \"zSYSAnalogic_UI_ShowInTable_Empty\", \"zSYSAnalogic_UI_ShowInTable_Global\" ) )}' SET [ProductTypeSubsetname] AS '{TM1SubsetToSet ( [Line Item BC P&L Input], IIF ( ISEMPTY([BC Product Metadata].([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version],[Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname],[Measures BC Product Metadata].[Product Type])), \"zSYSAnalogic_UI_ShowInTable_Empty\", [BC Product Metadata].([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version],[Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname],[Measures BC Product Metadata].[Product Type Subset]) ) )}' SELECT ( UNION([ProductTypeSubsetname],[GlobalOrEmptySubsetname], ALL) ) ON COLUMNS FROM [BC Line Item Comments] WHERE ([Draft].[$rocheDraftTable_open_version], [Product].[$rocheProductsTable_choose_productname], [Measures BC Line Item Comments].[hasComment])"}
adminPortalWidgetCatalogFilterGridParent: {"MDX":" SELECT NON EMPTY {TM1SORT( {Filter( {TM1DRILLDOWNMEMBER( { [zSYS Analogic UI Definition].[$selectedApplication] }, ALL, RECURSIVE )}, [zSYS Analogic UI Definition].CurrentMember.Level.Ordinal <> 0)}, ASC)} ON COLUMNS FROM [}ElementAttributes_zSYS Analogic UI Definition] WHERE ([}ElementAttributes_zSYS Analogic UI Definition].[Caption])"}
